c5 $5 ({The pointe is shown by} 35... Rd6 36. Qb3 Rd3 37. Bc3 $1 Qf6 38. Bf1 $1
{and the pin of Nf7 becomes fatal.}) 36. bxc5 bxc5 37. Bc3 Ra7 38. Qb3 $1 Kh8
39. Ne6 Qg8 40. Nxc5 Rd8 41. Bd5 {
